---
const waLink = 'https://wa.me/6281288045939?text=Halo%20Oriskin%2C%20saya%20sudah%20siap%20reservasi.%20Kapan%20bisa%3F';
---

<section class="promo" id="promo">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="promo-card reveal">
      <div class="promo-badge">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
        Promo Spesial Bulan Ini
      </div>
      <h2>Diskon Hingga <em>30%</em> untuk Perawatan Pertama</h2>
      <p>Dapatkan penawaran eksklusif untuk kunjungan pertama Anda. Reservasi sekarang dan nikmati perawatan premium dengan harga spesial.</p>
      <a href={waLink} class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Klaim Promo Sekarang
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      <p class="promo-terms">*Syarat dan ketentuan berlaku. Promo berlaku sampai akhir bulan ini.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .promo {
    padding: 96px 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .promo-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--charcoal) 0%, #2D3748 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 48px 32px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .promo-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -30%;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,122,90,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .promo-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30%;
    left: -20%;
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(110,127,99,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .promo-card > :global(*) {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .promo-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    background: rgba(201,122,90,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,122,90,0.3);
    border-radius: 60px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--terracotta-light);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .promo-card h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .promo-card h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta-light);
  }

  .promo-card > p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .promo-card .btn-primary {
    background: var(--terracotta);
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 18px 42px;
  }

  .promo-card .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--terracotta-light);
  }

  .promo-terms {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .promo-card {
      padding: 72px 64px;
    }
  }
</style>
